lly original story, with input from author Carl Hiaasen.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e“‘Razor Girl’ is a great novel for people who want to read it, but it’s kind of a break from the characters of the first [book],” Lawrence explains, “and we wanted to have some of the characters from the first season more front and center in the second” — including \u003ca href=\"https://tvline.com/t/natalie-martinez/\" id=\"auto-tag_natalie-martinez\" data-tag=\"natalie-martinez\"\u003eNatalie Martinez\u003c/a\u003e‘s Rosa. “[Season 2 is] an original story, but we’re all Carl Hiaasen aficionados — and, also, Carl consults on the show and has been helping us a ton.”\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1240\" height=\"840\" src=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg\" alt=\"Bad Monkey Season 2 Cast, Filming, \u0026#39;Razor Girl\u0026#39; Update — Release Date?\" srcset=\"https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg 1240w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=200,135 200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=300,203 300w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=768,520 768w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=1024,694 1024w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=148,100 148w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=600,406 600w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=276,187 276w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?resize=1000,677 1000w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bad-monkey-season-2-apple-tv-plus.jpg?